These are Puzzles for 4x3 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-1::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: baking, dancing, reading
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: disaster, spy, superhero
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: blues, folk, trance
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: bellflower, balloon-flower, sunflower
1. the person who growsbellflower is on the right of the fan of trance##1
2. the fan of blues is on the left of the person who growssunflower##1
3. the person who's hobby is baking is between the person watching spy movies and the person watching superhero movies##2
4. the person who growsbellflower is on the right of the person who's hobby is dancing##1
5. the fan of trance is the person watching spy movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |     3     |
| Hobby         | dancing | baking   | reading   |
| Movie-Genre   | spy     | disaster | superhero |
| Music-Genre   | trance  | blues    | folk      |
| Flower     | balloon-flower     | bellflower      | sunflower |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-2::.
There 3 different types of food: kale, raspberry, tomato
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: blues, gospel, soul
There are 3 different nationalities: australian, japanese, pakistani
The people use 3 different means of transport: bus, van, snowmobile
1. the fan of soul is on the left of the person driving the van##1
2. the pakistani is on the left of the fan of soul##1
3. the person eating raspberry is the pakistani##1
4. the person eating kale is the japanese##1
5. the person driving the bus is between the fan of gospel and the person eating tomato##2
6. the person eating tomato is the person driving the van##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |     3      |
| Food          | raspberry  | kale     | tomato     |
| Music-Genre   | gospel     | soul     | blues      |
| Nationality   | pakistani  | japanese | australian |
| Transport           | snowmobile | bus     | van       |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-3::.
There 3 different types of food: eggplant, kale, orange
3 different games are played: domino, monopoly, billiard
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: disaster, mystery, thriller
3 different pets are kept: chinchilla, goldfish, snake
1. the person playing domino is on the left of the person watching thriller movies##1
2. the owner of the chinchilla is between the person playing billiard and the person watching thriller movies##2
3. the person eating eggplant is on the far left##1
4. the owner of the goldfish is the person eating kale##1
5. the owner of the chinchilla is the person watching mystery movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |    3     |
| Food          | eggplant  | orange     | kale     |
| Game           | billiard | domino  | monopoly   |
| Movie-Genre   | disaster  | mystery    | thriller |
| Pet           | snake     | chinchilla | goldfish |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-4::.
There 3 different types of food: cherry, cucumber, raspberry
The people have 3 different jobs:  journalist, paramedic, scientist
3 different pets are kept: cat, chinchilla, guinea-pig
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: ritmeester, siglo, chaman
1. the ritmeester-smoker is on the right of the owner of the chinchilla##1
2. the person eating cucumber is on the right of the scientist##1
3. the person eating raspberry is between the paramedic and the owner of the cat##2
4. the person eating cucumber is the siglo-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1       |     2      |     3      |
| Food    | cherry       | raspberry  | cucumber   |
| Job     | paramedic    | scientist  | journalist |
| Pet     | chinchilla   | guinea-pig | cat        |
| Cigar   | chaman | ritmeester     | siglo      |

