1. the person who's birthday is in april is on the left of the person watching time-travel movies##1
2. the pilot is on the right of the owner of the pony##1
3. the nurse is between the person watching time-travel movies and the owner of the snake##2
4. the person who's birthday is in july is on the left of the person watching martial-arts movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
